    "in_trash": false,
    "type": "paragraph",
    "paragraph": {
      "rich_text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "The total journey took us about 30 hours. Sleep was had on the airplanes, although probably not enough. Upon arriving in Qatar, we were greeted by a full on rave under the teddy bear with the lampshade. Niklas was on the plane with us from South Africa. We meet Jess next to the party teddy and the excitement - or was it sleep deprivation - reaches an all time high. ",
            "link": null
          },
          "annotations": {
            "bold": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "underline": false,
            "code": false,
            "color": "default"
          },
          "plain_text": "The total journey took us about 30 hours. Sleep was had on the airplanes, although probably not enough. Upon arriving in Qatar, we were greeted by a full on rave under the teddy bear with the lampshade. Niklas was on the plane with us from South Africa. We meet Jess next to the party teddy and the excitement - or was it sleep deprivation - reaches an all time high. ",
